data.title: Airhead SHRED TIME Wakeboard
data.description: SHRED TIME is a lightweight twin tip freeride wakeboard designed to help youth riders of all levels excel at the sport. The continuous rocker is fast and forgiving with smooth pop. It’s 124cm long, perfect for youth riders up to 130 lbs. Two removable fiberglass reinforced nylon fins provide excellent tracking and carving.

data.title: Airhead Blast 2014 HD
data.description: You'll have a real blast on Airhead Blast! The 4 neoprene knuckle guards and deluxe nylon covered handles provide a sure and comfortable grip. The heavy-duty virgin PVC bladder has electronically welded seams and a Boston valve for quick inflating and deflating. Blast has a double stitched nylon cover, reinforced internal tow harness and a self-draining floor vent. You'll love the eye-catching graphics on this 1 rider 54˝ (deflated) round towable!
